{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were people working there without shirts, naked-- half-naked-- with huge tongs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would pick up this metal, put it in there, and then take it out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even the Nazis in the-- in the factory said that these workers should get a special ration.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, in the kitchen, while they were working, they could eat whatever they wanted, when they we were working there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they could not bring anything out of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, they were making, like I said-- they were making sausages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now these sausages, they were cooked in a huge kettle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, they made the sausage, and then they took the raw meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And put them into that kettle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they cooked them in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that water, usually, is thrown out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because that's just greasy water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they decided that that greasy water is a double ration for those people that worked so hard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once a week, I was assigned to go to that kitchen with a wagon and two horses-- a wagon-- a wagon-- is a wagon that was just with four wheels, and there was just some boards thrown over it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had no springs or anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called it a [NON-ENGLISH] wagon in Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got a permit to go, because I was a young guy and I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they let me do this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to go to that kitchen, every week, once a week, with two kettles-- army Army kettles, thermos kettles, you know, that get sealed, like they have in the army, where they bring the food for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to bring those kettles to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not allowed to go inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
